net.antidot.api.upload

Class Reply

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.antidot.api.upload.Reply

  • public class Reply
extends java.lang.Object
    Reply of uploaded documents.

    This reply is returned when documents are uploaded to specific PaF through Antidot Back Office.
